    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReplyAttachmentsMessage

    public class PostAttachmentsMessage
extends PostMessage
    A RuntimeAction that posts a message to a given Slack channel.

    This class relies on the SlackPlatform's Slack client and Slack bot API token to connect to the Slack API and post messages.

    Note: this class requires that its containing SlackPlatform has been loaded with a valid Slack bot API token in order to authenticate the bot and post messages.
